Age- must be in between (0-99), does
not allow null values


 alter table STUDENT add check(0<=age<100);
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.04 sec)


mysql> DESC STUDENT;
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field   | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
