| gender  | varchar(5)  | YES  |     | m       |       |
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)









Gender- default value is ‘m’



 ALTER TABLE STUDENT ALTER gender SET DEFAULT 'm';
